<p align="center"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">English Translation</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Chanting  thousand names, realization dawned good-souls, saved from the pall of  despair; Find a source of many graces in the benevolent Resident of  Himavan peaks. Pollen-spilling red Ashoka trees blossom with the hue of  the radiant Sun. Foolish bumble trees mistake them for fire and flee in  Piriti, -- O, Go to, my heart!</span></p></div><span class="article_separator">&nbsp;</span>
